commit.message:
Add offset option for /api/tasks (#998)

* Add offset option for /api/tasks

Resolves #989

* Set lower bound for offset param to 0

* Add unit tests for offset param

* Add support for sort_by parameter

* Replace dict with OrderedDict

Order of dict is can vary in different Python version, in order to make order deterministic I is replaced with OrderedDict.
